                    </div>
                    <div class="text-sm text-slate-600 font-medium">
                        Average cost
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none bg-white p-8 sm:p-12 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm"
            >
                <h2>What is an ECA?</h2>
                <p>
                    An <strong>Educational Credential Assessment (ECA)</strong> is
                    a document that verifies whether your foreign degree, diploma,
                    or certificate is equal to a Canadian credential. It's issued
                    by designated organizations approved by IRCC.
                </p>

                <h2>Do You Need an ECA for BC PNP?</h2>
                <p>ECA requirements depend on your situation:</p>

                <div class="not-prose overflow-x-auto my-6">
                    <table class="min-w-full text-left text-sm">
                        <thead class="bg-gray-100 border-b border-gray-200">
                            <tr>
                                <th class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-slate-900"
                                    >Scenario</th
                                >
                                <th class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-slate-900"
                                    >ECA Required?</th
                                >
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100">
                            <tr>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3"
                                    >Canadian degree/diploma</td
                                >
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-green-700 font-bold"
                                    >No</td
                                >
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3"
                                    >Foreign credential + BC PNP only</td
                                >
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-700 font-bold"
                                    >Recommended (for points)</td
                                >
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3"
                                    >Foreign credential + Express Entry BC</td
                                >
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-red-700 font-bold"
                                    >Yes (required for EE profile)</td
                                >
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3"
                                    >Regulated profession (nursing, engineering)</td
                                >
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-red-700 font-bold"
                                    >Yes (licensing requirement)</td
                                >
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>

                <h2>Designated ECA Organizations</h2>
                <p>IRCC recognizes these organizations for immigration ECAs:</p>

                <div class="not-prose overflow-x-auto my-6">
                    <table class="min-w-full text-left text-sm">
                        <thead class="bg-gray-100 border-b border-gray-200">
                            <tr>
                                <th class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-slate-900"
                                    >Organization</th
                                >
                                <th class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-slate-900"
                                    >Best For</th
                                >
                                <th class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-slate-900"
                                    >Processing Time</th
                                >
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100">
                            <tr class="bg-green-50">
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold"
                                    >WES (World Education Services)</td
                                >
                                <td class="px-4 py-3"
                                    >Most countries, fastest</td
                                >
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">7-20 business days</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold">IQAS</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">Alberta applicants</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">8-12 weeks</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold">ICAS</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">All countries</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">10-12 weeks</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold"
                                    >Comparative Education Service (UofT)</td
                                >
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">Academic purposes</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">12-16 weeks</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold"
                                    >MCC (Medical Council of Canada)</td
                                >
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">Physicians only</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">Varies</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold"
                                    >PEBC (Pharmacy Examining Board)</td
                                >
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">Pharmacists only</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">Varies</td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-xl text-sm border border-green-200 mb-8"
                >
                    <strong>üí° Recommendation:</strong> WES is the most popular choice
                    due to fast processing times and availability for most countries.
                    They also have agreements with many institutions for direct document
                    transfer.
                </div>

                <h2>How ECA Affects Your BC PNP Score</h2>
                <p>Your education level affects your SIRS score:</p>

                <div class="not-prose overflow-x-auto my-6">
                    <table class="min-w-full text-left text-sm">
                        <thead class="bg-gray-100 border-b border-gray-200">
                            <tr>
                                <th class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-slate-900"
